{"tid":337864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南蘇丹維和任務疑變主動戰鬥違憲   日本防衛相及多名自衛隊將領辭職","createTime":"2017-07-27T16:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T09:01:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c340d9699249dde6041aaa2d5e98897cd432c6d","tid":337864,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.read01.com/uploads/0FqsKJZjdz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.read01.com%2Fuploads%2F0FqsKJZjdz.jpg&h=d037b709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n27.07.2017 20:34<br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三下星期四改組內閣，日本傳媒報道，盛傳會被撤換的防衛相稻田朋美，將會辭職，為暪報自衛隊參與南蘇丹維和行動日誌，承擔責任。報道指，日本當局明日會公布暪報事件的調查報告，稻田明日會向安倍提交辭職信，職務可能由其他閣員暫時兼任。而自衛隊陸上幕僚長岡部俊哉，及防衛省事務次官黑江哲郎亦決定辭職。<br />\n<br />\n陸上自衛隊五月底結束在南蘇丹的聯合國維和行動後，自衛隊被揭發隱藏紀錄當地活動的工作日誌，當中顯示自衛隊曾經在南蘇丹首都朱巴發生激烈戰鬥，以及在戰鬥區域涉嫌從事違憲活動，自衛隊宣稱已銷毀日誌，但實際上仍然保留。稻田朋美否認她曾同意隱暪事件，亦不知道自衛隊將日誌保留。稻田亦因為在東京都議會選舉助選時失言，受到抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=954663&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fpage%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D954663%26csid%3D261_367&d=EMoiwHz2a7Hj8AURh6H2%2BDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4fd028d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/page/zh-tw/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=954663&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"5630604c264b6f39097d1cb27e5b8ff976027400","tid":337864,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:54:39.000Z","msg":"倭寇"},{"pid":"0f18cbc380476ae344b48a27c8d87ebc22e32ba3","tid":337864,"uid":51200,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>倭寇</blockquote><br />\n五毛發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c6f7a9cbd53d2760ef3530ab1c5eb5270458b4","tid":337864,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-